# TipGroup.Priority

**Enumeration**

Order priority for a [doc://com.apple.TipKit/documentation/TipKit/TipGroup].

## Declaration

```swift
enum Priority
```

## Enumeration Cases

- **TipGroup.Priority.firstAvailable**: Shows the first tip eligible for display.
- **TipGroup.Priority.ordered**: Shows an eligible tip when all of the previous tips have been [doc://com.apple.TipKit/documentation/TipKit/Tips/Status/invalidated(_:)].

## Conforms To

- Copyable
- Equatable
- Hashable
- Sendable
- SendableMetatype
